cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper involves developing approaches to automate the process of generating user interface code from a wireframe or paper mockup. This involves computer vision techniques and deep learning, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
